Meet <b>Kerri</b>, our citizen of the week!<br><br>This stylish girl lives at <a href='/home/?user=kitty0880'>31472 Glenwood Boulevard</a> in Golden Valley. Since moving in on December 7, 2005, she has kept those around her on their toes with her strong opinions and adventurous spirit.<br><br>At school she can be reserved in class, but when she does raise her hand she always has something interesting to say. She'll approach a problem from a perspective that sometimes the teacher hasn't even considered. And when it comes to computers, Kerri is the girl who helps her classmates work through their problems.<br><br>Kerri is good at thinking outside of the box, and her fashion choices and diverse interests show how hard it is to categorize her. She is truly an individual, loving techno music as much as she loves playing basketball, and she is certain to find new things to excel at as she continues to live in Millsberry. You might even say her friends envy her for being good at everything!  <br><br>In 2007 she looks forward to acquiring more interesting furniture for her house, and may get a new pet. A new year brings new possibilities, and Kerri is ready to take on new challenges and make her mark.<br><br>Thanks for being a good citizen, Kerri, and congrats on being named Millsberry's citizen of the week!</div>
